fields.title: Nutritionish Resource
fields.description:
Nutritionist Resource is an online web directory listing nutritionists all over the UK.

Each nutritionist has a profile indicating background, specialisms, qualifications and professional registrations.

The site also provides information covering areas that nutritionists can assist with, advice about good nutrition for optimum health for sports people, as well as a blog about the latest health news.

Email Nutritionist Resource for more information.

fields.title: Active Sports Bras
fields.description:
Active Sports Bras offer a wide range of top branded sports bras at discounted prices.

Enter the code CSHC10 at checkout in order to receive a further 10% off already reduced prices as well as free delivery.

fields.title: Injury Active Clinic
fields.description:
Injury Active offer injury assessment, treatment, sports massage and rehab. Check out their website for more details.

Cambridge South Hockey Club members are eligible for a 10% discount off all services.

fields.title: Cambridge Sports Massage
fields.description: Enter the code CSHOCKEY when booking online to receive a 10% discount.

fields.title: MiSEC
fields.description:
Run by our own Laurie Haslop, MiSEC solve your security weaknesses for residential and commercial organisations.

10% discount to members and those associated with the club. A contribution will also be made to the club's social budget by MiSEC, whch will go towards club social events thorugh the season. 

0203 432 4139

fields.title: The Grove, Cromer
fields.description:
Managed by our own Chris Graveling, The Grove in Cromer, Norfolk are offering dinner, bed and breakfast for £130 (down from £150) to all CSHC members from October 2014 to the end of March 2015.

Offer excludes the period from 21st Dec 2014 to 6th Jan 2015.
